Module org.uclouvain.visualsearchtree

module org.uclouvain.visualsearchtree

  • Installation

    Step 1. Add the JitPack repository to your build file

    INTEGRATION CODE

    
allprojects {
    repositories {
        ...
        maven { url 'https://jitpack.io' }
    }
}
    Code copié

    Step 2. Add the dependency

    INTEGRATION CODE

    
dependencies {
    implementation 'com.github.pschaus:visualsearchtree:'
}
    Code copié

    Step 1. Add the JitPack repository to your build file

    INTEGRATION CODE

    
<repositories>
    <repository>
        <id>jitpack.io</id>
        <url>https://jitpack.io</url>
    </repository>
</repositories>
    Code copié

    Step 2. Add the dependency

    INTEGRATION CODE

    
<dependency>
    <groupId>com.github.pschaus</groupId>
    <artifactId>visualsearchtree</artifactId>
    <version></version>
</dependency>
    Code copié

    Step 1. Add the JitPack repository to your build file

    INTEGRATION CODE

    

resolvers += "jitpack" at "https://jitpack.io"
    Code copié

    Step 2. Add the dependency

    INTEGRATION CODE

    

libraryDependencies += "com.github.pschaus" % "visualsearchtree" % ""
    Code copié

    Step 1. Add the JitPack repository to your build file

    INTEGRATION CODE

    

:repositories [["jitpack" "https://jitpack.io"]]
    Code copié

    Step 2. Add the dependency

    INTEGRATION CODE

    

:dependencies [[com.github.pschaus/visualsearchtree ""]]
    Code copié

    You can also refers to this link to include minicp in your project: https://jitpack.io/#pschaus/visualsearchtree/v1.0
